episodes.title: We Investigated The Cult of Scientology (Police Called!)
episodes.description:
We investigated the Cult of Scientology and tried to find Shelly Miscavige, we were followed, watched, and harassed by Scientology security. This is the strangest religion because of their extreme secrecy nobody knows what these people are doing all day long and they have taken over Clearwater Florida.

#scientology #scientologycult
